name: NLM Lung X Rays
description:
The original  public dataset is found [here](https://ceb.nlm.nih.gov/repositories/tuberculosis-chest-x-ray-image-data-sets/). This dataset is for education purpose only.

For further information regarding the dataset, see [this faq](https://openi.nlm.nih.gov/faq.php).
